1796   4A62             ; Will return a zero terminated string @ HL that can be printed
1797   4A62             ; Will return the value in DE
1798   4A62             CHECKTIMEOUT:
1799   4A62                 CLEAR_UART
1799   4A62 3E 14       >    ld  a,20
