4085   55A8             ;        DE = Number of urgent available incoming bytes
4086   55A8             ;        IX = Available free space in the output buffer
4087   55A8             ;             (0FFFFh = infinite)
4088   55A8             ;
4089   55A8             ;Connection information block consists of:
4090   55A8             ;
4091   55A8             ;    +0 (4): Remote IP address
4092   55A8             ;    +4 (2): Remote port
4093   55A8             ;    +6 (2): Local port
