4626   5898             ;===  TCPIP_CONFIG_AUTOIP  ===
4627   5898             ;=============================
4628   5898             ;Enable or disable the automatic IP addresses retrieval.
4629   5898             ;
4630   5898             ;Input:  A = 25
4631   5898             ;        B = 0: Get current configuration
4632   5898             ;            1: Set configuration
4633   5898             ;        C = Configuration to set (only if B=1):
4634   5898             ;            bit 0: Set to automatically retrieve
